-- Migration 17: Re-define context_config with OVERWRITE + FLEXIBLE.
-- Migration 15 defined the field without FLEXIBLE (SurrealDB silently strips
-- arbitrary nested keys on SCHEMAFULL tables).
-- Migration 16 used IF NOT EXISTS which is a no-op when the field already
-- exists, so the type was never corrected on existing databases.
-- OVERWRITE forces the field definition to be replaced regardless.

DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE context_config ON TABLE notebook FLEXIBLE TYPE option<object>;
